{"tid":1118373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斯里蘭卡連環爆炸　確認至少1名中國人死亡","createTime":"2019-04-21T11:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T15:09:11.000Z","uid":41404,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0158aabb692be872e6cb3ce20695ce69a4172771","tid":1118373,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"中國傳媒報道，斯里蘭卡連環爆炸事件中，已經確認有1名中國人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n當地已經先後發生8次爆炸，造成超過150人死亡，幾百人受傷。國防部長已經宣布晚上宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，死者包括至少35名外國人，包括美國、英國同荷蘭遊客。另外有4名中國人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n有官員相信表示，部分爆炸是自殺式襲擊。暫時未有組織承認責任。當地傳媒報告，當局已經鎖定兩疑犯。由於是復活節，大批信眾到教堂出席活動。<br />\n<br />\n總理譴責襲擊是懦夫行為，又與軍方高層召開緊急會議。多國領袖同教宗方濟各亦譴責襲擊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1453866-20190421.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1453866-20190421.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=8976d54e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1453866-20190421.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=86423334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1453866-20190421.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b1ce53511ccaffeee68b13dea77c6c370ff28366","tid":1118373,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:25:00.000Z","msg":"快撚啲雖軟必豬"},{"pid":"c835bcec167d088247dcb227a021c8ef374e2a81","tid":1118373,"uid":54733,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T11:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://wmoov.com/assets/movie/photo/201504/3b87e950352ac65c00f01e33f8f2b21192138afc5B15D_1427876201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwmoov.com%2Fassets%2Fmovie%2Fphoto%2F201504%2F3b87e950352ac65c00f01e33f8f2b21192138afc5B15D_1427876201.jpg&h=e3fe3c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5iCGEa7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u